======================================
Eclipse styles and other files
======================================

NOTE : this is note definitive, try it out and add what you think is useful to have

======================================
clean_code_style_templates.xml
======================================
this file is a specification of the normal eclipse 3.7 templates with the following changes 
- 2 chars instead of tabs
- removed 1 empty line between every single member variable

it is nice to have red comments, unfortunately can be done only manually
go to Window -> preferences -> Syntax Coloring


======================================
luigi_shortcut_configuration.csv
======================================
my personl configuration of shortcuts

- ctrl+J  : run unit test (replace incremental search though)
- ctrl+up + ctrl+up : copy selected line up
- ctrl+down + ctrl+down : copy selected line down

